Class ProjectConfigInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.cayenne.project.ProjectConfigInfo
Deprecated. since 3.0. ProjectConfigurator approach turned out to be not usable, and is in fact rarely used (if ever). It will be removed in subsequent releases. 

public class ProjectConfigInfo
extends Object

Stores project information necessary to reconfigure existing projects.
